OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5F'Head-in-sand' Birmingham  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fwas equal pay 'outlier'    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Birmingham City Council's financial    
OL,6, crisis was down to "burying its head in
OL,7, the sand" over equal pay liability, a  
OL,8, lawyer who represented claimants said. 
OL,10,FThe council has already paid out more  
OL,11,Fthan #1bn in compensation to underpaid 
OL,12,Fworkers.                               
OL,14,FBut on Tuesday it declared itself      
OL,15,Feffectively bankrupt and linked the    
OL,16,Fsituation to further equal pay         
OL,17,Fliability of #760m.                    
OL,19,FThe council previously apologised for  
OL,20,Fnot getting the issue under control.   
